{"tid":2044273,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"《國王的餐單》氣炸鍋燒腩仔","createTime":"2020-05-31T04:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T15:50:32.000Z","uid":205222,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f89ed752a8ca60ba166c44d196a39b613187b0e8","tid":2044273,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"今次整無疏針版，因為隻手岩岩傷左用唔到力，<br />\n有啲人話一定要疏針，其實唔疏針個皮都好脆，不過唔疏針就無左皮上面一個個小氣泡既視覺效果，<br />\n簡單d講無咁靚<br />\n我用既係黑毛豬五花腩，唔使出水，如果用普通新鮮豬肉，係一定要出水<br />\n首先叫檔口幫你燒皮刮毛，返到屋企洗乾淨<br />\n用平時食飯既飯盒，放d醃料落去，<br />\n我落左紹興酒，雞汁，鹽，生抽，糖，份量隨心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHbeKWi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHbeKWi.png&h=1a284410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整好醃料之後，將舊四方形既五花腩係底部介三下，一陣炸完會易切啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xOVSwCi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxOVSwCi.png&h=65dc0b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再放入飯盒醃，豬皮要向上，唔可以沾上任何水份/醬料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1yT0wh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1yT0wh.png&h=42d04e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放入雪櫃，雪兩晚，等抽乾水份<br />\n兩晚之後<br />\n預熱氣炸鍋200度30min<br />\n雪完後既五花腩應該係硬棚棚，無哂水份，跟住係豬皮上掃一層白醋，再舖鹽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DiNxwDz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDiNxwDz.png&h=ce988270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預熱完，放入氣炸鍋，200度20min<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JKskxA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3JKskxA.png&h=d93c5111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20分鍾後，開蓋，刮走啲鹽（唔好掉左落啲肉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）再用180度焗15min (份量大既五花腩要焗內啲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUhNkzR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUhNkzR.png&h=a6233410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成後，<br />\n唔記得影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺出黎通風位攤一陣，個皮會更脆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1h9Tf8H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1h9Tf8H.png&h=b8857da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肥胖人士忌食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af91e9696142e209344044f0b156ab34125b930","tid":2044273,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"燒腩仔靚<br />\n肥瘦適中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e52f3317db982279f9cb4c8474ff93342754d38","tid":2044273,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2af91e9696142e209344044f0b156ab34125b930","tid":2044273,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"燒腩仔靚<br />\n肥瘦適中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"呢舊黑毛豬黎，唔使出水都肉質鮮甜"},{"pid":"ebc959ce95fcfa7082255ef32cf815dd15764067","tid":2044273,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"氣炸師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c12160d3bf17a15ce3919a20087450ad6756448","tid":2044273,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc959ce95fcfa7082255ef32cf815dd15764067","tid":2044273,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"氣炸師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"太方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e8fd239ba8b1ae45f55fb4050f2943faec525e","tid":2044273,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc959ce95fcfa7082255ef32cf815dd15764067","tid":2044273,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"氣炸師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:51